In reality,

and because their graduate students will follow them here.

And we network it right back in all over Europe, all over the world.

And in my judgment, Texas, above all other states, has the best opportunity to lead for America.
And Houston, above all other places in Texas, is the right place.
And if Houston and Dallas can ever get over their local syndrome of the Bedouin philosophy of competing with one another, the Houston-Dallas region would be one of the heartthrobs of the world.

Because I don't see anybody else working on it.

That's interesting.
That's good.
